{"tid":429901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有無人記得當年用7000蚊係Sd高達online入面買自由高達既肥仔","createTime":"2017-10-09T10:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T11:06:28.000Z","uid":45857,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f65a3ad3b90fe2e1b3e9daabf527e49de6c7b7b6","tid":429901,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"今時今日真係世界變, 想當年係online game度買點買200蚊, 都肉赤左成個月, 呢位人兄當年用7000蚊買虛擬角色, 無論係高登定係其他網上論壇, 以至現實中Fd吹水, 大家都好有共識咁群起恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果過左唔夠十年, 而家香港差大部分有玩手機遊戲既人每個月課番一百幾十係等閒事, 日本班youtuber玩得仲勁, 時不時就會見到課金十萬円既抽卡片, 諷刺地十萬円正好係港紙7000蚊左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7013d25c3892b056a5fa35aefe97a353c29b72","tid":429901,"uid":78113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e80c2a1d322c79db4e691b99e842f3f190d84d7","tid":429901,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:26:41.000Z","msg":"條友太高調, 每次出場都比人圍住嚟攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f33e09dbf3518976d1da4ad55d3356a3297fd95","tid":429901,"uid":112198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:06:28.000Z","msg":"出g圖果時即刻9衝，結果幾年後就派免費突2。"}]}